"1/2 cup plus 2 Tbsp. honey","1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme","8 cups water (2 cups at room temperature, 6 cups boiling)","6 cups fresh or frozen peach slices","10  regular-size black tea bags","2 tablespoons fresh lemon juice","9 ounces bourbon, optional","  Thyme sprigs and lemon slices, for garnish"